{
	"nodes":[
		{"id":"sector3-title","type":"text","text":"# Sector 3: Component Architecture\n\n**Detailed Component Analysis**\n\nResponsibilities, contracts, integration points, and test coverage","x":50,"y":50,"width":600,"height":100,"color":"#4a90e2"},
		{"id":"components-grid","type":"text","text":"## Core Components Reference\n\n| Component | Primary File | Status | Critical? |\n|-----------|-------------|--------|-----------|\n| [[GlobalAgentContainer]] | `core/runtime/global_agent.py` | ✓ Active | HIGH |\n| [[AgentOrchestrator]] | `core/orchestrator/agent_orchestrator.py` | ✓ Active | HIGH |\n| [[SmartLLM]] | `core/llm/smart_llm.py` | ✓ Active | HIGH |\n| [[PlanningEngine]] | `core/tasks/` | ✓ Active | MEDIUM |\n| [[TaskStore]] | `core/tasks/task_store.py` | ✓ Active | MEDIUM |\n| [[TaskWorker]] | `core/tasks/task_worker.py` | ✓ Active | MEDIUM |\n| [[HybridMemoryManager]] | `core/memory/hybrid_memory_manager.py` | ✓ Active | HIGH |\n| [[ExecutionRouter]] | `core/orchestrator/execution_router.py` | ✓ Active | MEDIUM |\n\n### Legend\n- **Status:** ✓ = Active, ⚠️ = Has Issues, ❌ = Deprecated\n- **Critical:** EXTREME, HIGH, MEDIUM, LOW\n- **Change Risk:** >100 lines = approval required","x":20,"y":650,"width":730,"height":280,"color":"#f5f5f5"},
		{"id":"component-chain","type":"text","text":"```mermaid\ngraph LR\n    subgraph Component Interaction Flow\n        direction LR\n        User[User Message] --> Orchestrator[AgentOrchestrator]\n        Orchestrator --> Router[ExecutionRouter]\n        Router --> Intent{Intent Classification}\n        \n        Intent -->|CONVERSATION| ChatLLM[SmartLLM CHAT]\n        Intent -->|TOOL_ACTION| ToolLLM[SmartLLM TOOL]\n        Intent -->|MEMORY_QUERY| PlannerLLM[SmartLLM PLANNER]\n        Intent -->|TASK_REQUEST| Planner[PlanningEngine]\n        \n        Planner --> TaskStore[(TaskStore)]\n        TaskStore --> Worker[TaskWorker]\n        \n        ChatLLM --> Response[Response]\n        ToolLLM --> Tools[Tool Execution]\n        Tools --> Response\n        PlannerLLM --> Memory[HybridMemoryManager]\n        Memory --> Response\n        Worker --> Tools\n        \n        style User fill:#4a90e2\n        style Orchestrator fill:#5ba3f5\n        style Router fill:#6cb5f8\n        style Intent fill:#7dc7fb\n        style ChatLLM fill:#8ed9fe\n        style ToolLLM fill:#8ed9fe\n        style PlannerLLM fill:#8ed9fe\n        style Planner fill:#8ed9fe\n        style Response fill:#b0fdff\n    end\n```","x":800,"y":170,"width":2520,"height":450,"color":"#e8f4fd"},
		{"id":"global-container-graph","type":"text","text":"```mermaid\nclassDiagram\n    class GlobalAgentContainer {\n        <<Singleton>>\n        +get_orchestrator()\n        +initialize_resources()\n        +resources\n    }\n    \n    class HybridMemoryManager {\n        +vector_search()\n        +keyword_search()\n        +small_talk_bypass()\n    }\n    \n    class SQLiteTaskStore {\n        +persist_task()\n        +get_task()\n        +update_status()\n    }\n    \n    class ProviderFactory {\n        +get_llm_provider()\n        +get_stt_provider()\n        +get_tts_provider()\n    }\n    \n    class ToolManager {\n        +register_tool()\n        +get_tools()\n        +execute_tool()\n    }\n    \n    GlobalAgentContainer --> HybridMemoryManager : contains\n    GlobalAgentContainer --> SQLiteTaskStore : contains\n    GlobalAgentContainer --> ProviderFactory : contains\n    GlobalAgentContainer --> ToolManager : contains\n    \n    style GlobalAgentContainer fill:#4a90e2\n    style HybridMemoryManager fill:#5ba3f5\n    style SQLiteTaskStore fill:#6cb5f8\n    style ProviderFactory fill:#7dc7fb\n    style ToolManager fill:#8ed9fe\n```","x":50,"y":170,"width":700,"height":450},
		{"id":"4e0235b936c3a16c","type":"text","text":"```mermaid\nclassDiagram\n    class GlobalAgentContainer {\n        <<Singleton>>\n        +get_orchestrator()\n        +initialize_resources()\n        +resources\n    }\n    \n    class HybridMemoryManager {\n        +vector_search()\n        +keyword_search()\n        +small_talk_bypass()\n    }\n    \n    class SQLiteTaskStore {\n        +persist_task()\n        +get_task()\n        +update_status()\n    }\n    \n    class ProviderFactory {\n        +get_llm_provider()\n        +get_stt_provider()\n        +get_tts_provider()\n    }\n    \n    class ToolManager {\n        +register_tool()\n        +get_tools()\n        +execute_tool()\n    }\n    \n    GlobalAgentContainer --> HybridMemoryManager : contains\n    GlobalAgentContainer --> SQLiteTaskStore : contains\n    GlobalAgentContainer --> ProviderFactory : contains\n    GlobalAgentContainer --> ToolManager : contains\n    \n    style GlobalAgentContainer fill:#4a90e2\n    style HybridMemoryManager fill:#5ba3f5\n    style SQLiteTaskStore fill:#6cb5f8\n    style ProviderFactory fill:#7dc7fb\n    style ToolManager fill:#8ed9fe\n```","x":20,"y":170,"width":730,"height":450},
		{"id":"smartllm-details","type":"text","text":"## SmartLLM Component Deep Dive\n\n**File:** `core/llm/smart_llm.py`\n\n### Responsibilities\n1. **Provider abstraction** - Groq, OpenAI, etc.\n2. **Role management** - CHAT/TOOL/PLANNER/WORKER\n3. **Context building** - Within token budget\n4. **Tool schema** - Format per provider\n5. **Response parsing** - Extract tool calls\n\n### Role Configurations\n| Role | Access Tools | Access Memory | Temp | Purpose |\n|------|-------------|---------------|------|---------|\n| CHAT | ❌ No | ❌ No | 0.7 | Conversational |\n| TOOL_ACTION | ✅ Yes | ❌ No | 0.3 | Tool execution |\n| PLANNER | ❌ No | ✅ Yes | 0.5 | Task planning |\n| WORKER | ✅ Yes | ✅ Yes | 0.4 | Background tasks |\n\n### Issue: Schema Mismatch\n🔴 [[LLM Tool-Call Schema Mismatch]] noted\n- SmartLLM ↔ LiveKit ↔ Worker schemas inconsistent\n- Current hack: `strict_tool_schema = False`\n- Issue: ongoing race condition\n\n**Test:** test_smart_llm.py\n**Related:** [[Role-Based LLM System]] | [[ExecutionRouter]]","x":780,"y":680,"width":700,"height":380,"color":"#fff3e0"},
		{"id":"task-system-details","type":"text","text":"## Task System Deep Dive\n\n### PlanningEngine\n**Purpose:** Break complex requests → atomic tasks\n\n**Task Specification:**\n- Duration: 2-5 minutes each\n- Contains:\n  - Exact file paths\n  - Complete code specifications\n  - Verification steps\n  - Dependencies\n\n**Example:**\n```python\ntask = {\n    'id': 'task_001',\n    'duration': '3 min',\n    'file_paths': ['core/runtime/global_agent.py'],\n    'code_spec': 'Add get_orchestrator() classmethod',\n    'verification': ['import test', 'console test'],\n    'depends_on': []\n}\n```\n\n### TaskStore (SQLite)\n**Schema:**\n```sql\nCREATE TABLE tasks (\n    id TEXT PRIMARY KEY,\n    status TEXT, -- PENDING/RUNNING/COMPLETED/FAILED\n    file_paths TEXT,\n    code_spec TEXT,\n    verification TEXT\n)```\n\n**WAL Mode:** Enabled for high concurrency\n\n### TaskWorker Background Loop\n```python\nwhile True:\n    task = poll_task_store(status=RUNNING)\n    if task:\n        execute_task(task)\n        update_status(COMPLETED or FAILED)\n    sleep(poll_interval)\n```\n\n**Benefits:**\n- Crash recovery (tasks persisted)\n- Parallel execution\n- Status tracking\n- Retry on failure\n\n**Related:** [[Task Worker System]] | [[PlanningEngine]] | [[TaskStore]]","x":1540,"y":680,"width":700,"height":380,"color":"#e8f8f5"}
	],
	"edges":[]
}